description:
Today I test the world’s cheapest meals - but they actually taste good, my friends.
No prison food, no sadness soup. Just real Slav budget cuisine that even babushka approves.

On the menu:
🥔 0.15€ Onion Pasta
🥬 0.40€ Village Soup
🥟 0.33€ Cheater Dumplings
All cheap. All delicious. All possible even during 2025 inflation.

If you like this style of budget cooking, tell me in comments! More Slav survival recipes coming soon.
Stay cheeki breeki! 🥔

Music by Boris & The Balalaikas
